{"url": "https://www.ics.uci.edu/~kobsa/courses/ICS104/course-notes/menu-overview.htm", "content": "<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//w3c//dtd html 4.0 transitional//en\">\n<html><head>\n\n\n\n\n   <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=iso-8859-1\">\n   <meta name=\"GENERATOR\" content=\"Mozilla/4.71 (Macintosh; I; PPC) [Netscape]\"><title>Menu-Based Interaction -- Overview</title></head><body bgcolor=\"#ffffff\">\n<h2> <font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font size=\"+4\">Menu-based Interaction -- Overview</font></font></h2>&nbsp; \n<h4> <font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font size=\"+3\">3 basic activities:</font></font></h4><ul> \n<li> <font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font size=\"+2\">Navigation (in menu hierarchy, \ninformation resource, etc.)</font></font></li><li> <font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font size=\"+2\">Selection \n(of data, parameters, etc.)</font></font></li><li> <font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font size=\"+2\">Activation \n(of programs, documents, etc.)</font></font></li></ul><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font size=\"+3\"><b>Selection \nmade</b> </font><font size=\"+2\">through mouse, number/character keys, function keys, \ncursor keys plus return key, rotating cursor symbol plus return key, touching \non the screen, etc.</font></font> <br> <font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font size=\"+2\">Special \ncase: \"analog\" menus </font></font><font><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\"><a href=\"menu-types-examples.jpg\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"></span><a href=\"sliders.jpeg\"><img style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 11px; height: 11px;\" src=\"../../../Graphics%20Templates/Diamonds/Di-red.gif\" alt=\"The linked image shows several types of &quot;analog&quot; slikders\"></a></a></font></font></font> <h4> <font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font size=\"+3\">Types \nof menus </font><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\"><a href=\"menu-types-examples.jpg\"><img src=\"../../../Graphics%20Templates/Diamonds/Di-red.gif\" alt=\"The linked image shows several types of menus, namely textual menus, a menu that can be activated with function keys, a pulldown menu, and a graphical menu\" border=\"0\" height=\"11\" width=\"11\"></a></font></font></h4><ul> \n<li> <font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font size=\"+2\">Textual menus</font></font></li><li> \n<font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font size=\"+2\">Graphical menus (icons)</font></font></li>\n<li> \n<font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font size=\"+2\">Combination of text and graphics</font></font></li><br> \n&nbsp; <li> <font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font size=\"+2\">Linear menus</font></font></li>\n  <li> \n<font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font size=\"+2\">Menus with spatial layout</font></font><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\"> </font></font><a href=\"nonspatial-menu.png\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"4\"><font face=\"Wingdings\" size=\"5\"><img style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 21px; height: 27px;\" alt=\"Thumb pointing down\" src=\"../../../graphics/thumb_down-small.png\"></font></font></font></font></a><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\"> </font></font><big><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\" size=\"5\"><big><a href=\"spatial-menu.png\"><img style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 21px; height: 27px;\" alt=\"Error &quot;are you sure?&quot;\" src=\"../../../graphics/thumb_up.gif\"></a> </big></font></big><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\"><a href=\"coders-screen.jpg\"><img style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 11px; height: 11px;\" src=\"../../../Graphics%20Templates/Diamonds/Di-red.gif\" alt=\"The linked image shows a menu with spatial layout in the shape of a table.\"></a></font></font></li>\n  <font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\"> </font></font></ul><big><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\" size=\"5\"><big><a href=\"spatial-menu.png\"></a></big></font></big>\n<ul>\n  <font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\"> </font></font> \n</ul>\n<big><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\" size=\"5\"><big><a href=\"error-are-you-sure.jpg\"></a></big></font></big> \n<ul>\n<li> <font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font size=\"+2\">Static menus (e.g., \nmenu bar)</font></font></li><li> <font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font size=\"+2\">Pull-down \nmenu</font></font></li>\n  <li> <font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font size=\"+2\">Pop-up \nmenus</font></font></li>\n</ul><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica;\"></span>\n<ul>\n  <li> <font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font size=\"+2\">Single vs. multiple choice </font></font><a href=\"menus-single-multiple-choice.png\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"> <font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\"><img style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 11px; height: 11px;\" src=\"../../../Graphics%20Templates/Diamonds/Di-red.gif\" alt=\"The linked image shows hierarchical table-like menu. Depending on what the user selects in the first column, the items in the second and third column change.\"></font></font></font></font></font></a></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li> <font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font size=\"+2\">Isolated \nmenus</font></font></li>\n  <li> <font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font size=\"+2\">Connected \nmenus (mostly hierarchical menus) </font><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\"><a href=\"menu-hierarchical1.jpg\"><img src=\"../../../Graphics%20Templates/Diamonds/Di-red.gif\" alt=\"The linked image shows a hierarchical menu where the lower-level menus are aligned to the right of the corresponding superordinate menu.\" border=\"0\" height=\"11\" width=\"11\"></a></font> <a href=\"menu-hierarchical-relative.jpg\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\"><img style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 11px; height: 11px;\" src=\"../../../Graphics%20Templates/Diamonds/Di-red.gif\" alt=\"The linked image shows hierarchical table-like menu. Depending on what the user selects in the first column, the items in the second and third column change.\"></font></font></font></a></font></font></li>\n\n</ul>\n\n<ul> \n<li><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font size=\"+2\">Pie menus</font></font> <font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font size=\"+2\"></font><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\"><a href=\"pie-menus.jpg\"><img src=\"../../../Graphics%20Templates/Diamonds/Di-red.gif\" alt=\"The linked image shows a hierarchical menu where the lower-level menus are aligned to the right of the corresponding superordinate menu.\" border=\"0\" height=\"11\" width=\"11\"></a></font></font></font></li></ul>\n\n</body></html>", "encoding": "ascii"}